{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782575908557,"sessionID":"ses_0f633c972ffekahfiXQPo6WHxi","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"tool_1mdBObWTOdFCIcoATeTcEv2m","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/design/008-sk-design-parent/031-design-context-benchmark/runs/kimi-A/card.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"nl\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Anobel – Bestellimieten</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --blue: #06458c;\n      --blue-deep: #053b77;\n      --blue-darker: #043367;\n      --tint-100: #f2f3f6;\n      --tint-200: #e7e9ee;\n      --tint-300: #cbd0dc;\n      --green: #367e39;\n      --red: #c9140f;\n      --gold: #dbab00;\n      --white: #fefefe;\n      --black: #0a0a0a;\n      --text: #0a1a2f;\n      --muted: #787878;\n    }\n\n    * {\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    body {\n      background: var(--tint-100);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-family: \"Hanken Grotesk\", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, sans-serif;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      line-height: 1.35;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      min-height: 100vh;\n      padding: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .card {\n      width: 560px;\n      height: 480px;\n      background: var(--white);\n      border: 1px solid var(--tint-300);\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .card-header {\n      background: var(--blue);\n      color: var(--white);\n      padding: 18px 20px 16px;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n\n    .card-header h1 {\n      font-size: 20px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      letter-spacing: -0.2px;\n      margin-bottom: 2px;\n    }\n\n    .card-header p {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: var(--tint-200);\n      font-weight: 400;\n    }\n\n    .summary {\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 12px;\n      padding: 16px 20px 14px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--tint-200);\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n\n    .summary-item {\n      flex: 1;\n    }\n\n    .summary-item dt {\n      font-size: 11px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.4px;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n\n    .summary-item dd {\n      font-size: 18px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--text);\n    }\n\n    .summary-item.positive dd {\n      color: var(--green);\n    }\n\n    .alert {\n      background: var(--red);\n      color: var(--white);\n      padding: 12px 20px;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 10px;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n\n    .alert-icon {\n      width: 18px;\n      height: 18px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      border: 1.5px solid var(--white);\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      font-size: 11px;\n      line-height: 1;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n\n    .alert-detail {\n      font-weight: 400;\n      color: var(--tint-200);\n      margin-left: auto;\n    }\n\n    .locations {\n      flex: 1;\n      overflow: auto;\n      padding: 8px 0 0;\n    }\n\n    table {\n      width: 100%;\n      border-collapse: collapse;\n      text-align: left;\n    }\n\n    thead {\n      position: sticky;\n      top: 0;\n      z-index: 1;\n    }\n\n    th {\n      background: var(--tint-100);\n      color: var(--muted);\n      font-size: 10px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n      padding: 8px 20px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--tint-300);\n    }\n\n    td {\n      padding: 14px 20px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--tint-200);\n      vertical-align: top;\n    }\n\n    tr:last-child td {\n      border-bottom: none;\n    }\n\n    tr.alert-row td {\n      background: rgba(201, 20, 15, 0.05);\n      border-left: 3px solid var(--red);\n      padding-left: 17px;\n    }\n\n    tr.warning-row td {\n      border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);\n      padding-left: 17px;\n    }\n\n    .location-name {\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--text);\n    }\n\n    .location-meta {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin-top: 2px;\n    }\n\n    .amount {\n      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n      font-weight: 600;\n    }\n\n    .amount.positive {\n      color: var(--green);\n    }\n\n    .amount.negative {\n      color: var(--red);\n    }\n\n    .amount.warning {\n      color: var(--gold);\n    }\n\n    .badge {\n      display: inline-block;\n      font-size: 10px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.4px;\n      padding: 2px 6px;\n      border-radius: 2px;\n      margin-left: 6px;\n    }\n\n    .badge-alert {\n      background: var(--red);\n      color: var(--white);\n    }\n\n    .badge-warning {\n      background: var(--gold);\n      color: var(--text);\n    }\n\n    .card-footer {\n      padding: 12px 20px;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--tint-200);\n      font-size: 11px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <article class=\"card\">\n    <header class=\"card-header\">\n      <h1>Bestellimieten</h1>\n      <p>Per schip / locatie · Periode: Q2 2026</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <dl class=\"summary\">\n      <div class=\"summary-item\">\n        <dt>Totaallimiet</dt>\n        <dd>€ 35.000,00</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"summary-item\">\n        <dt>Totaal besteed</dt>\n        <dd>€ 31.890,50</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"summary-item positive\">\n        <dt>Resterend</dt>\n        <dd>€ 3.109,50</dd>\n      </div>\n    </dl>\n\n    <div class=\"alert\" role=\"alert\">\n      <span class=\"alert-icon\">!</span>\n      <span>Overschrijding op MV Zeeland</span>\n      <span class=\"alert-detail\">€ 450,00 boven limiet</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"locations\">\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>Locatie / Schip</th>\n            <th>Limiet</th>\n            <th>Besteed</th>\n            <th>Resterend</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>\n              <div class=\"location-name\">Amsterdam</div>\n              <div class=\"location-meta\">MV Rotterdam</div>\n            </td>\n            <td class=\"amount\">€ 12.000,00</td>\n            <td class=\"amount\">€ 9.240,50</td>\n            <td class=\"amount positive\">€ 2.759,50</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"alert-row\">\n            <td>\n              <div class=\"location-name\">Rotterdam</div>\n              <div class=\"location-meta\">MV Zeeland</div>\n            </td>\n            <td class=\"amount\">€ 8.000,00</td>\n            <td class=\"amount negative\">€ 8.450,00</td>\n            <td class=\"amount negative\">− € 450,00 <span class=\"badge badge-alert\">Alert</span></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"warning-row\">\n            <td>\n              <div class=\"location-name\">Antwerpen</div>\n              <div class=\"location-meta\">MV IJssel</div>\n            </td>\n            <td class=\"amount\">€ 15.000,00</td>\n            <td class=\"amount warning\">€ 14.200,00</td>\n            <td class=\"amount warning\">€ 800,00 <span class=\"badge badge-warning\">Bijna</span></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer class=\"card-footer\">\n      Limieten worden dagelijks gesynchroniseerd vanuit het hoofdadministratiesysteem.\n    </footer>\n  </article>\n</body>\n</html>\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/design/008-sk-design-parent/031-design-context-benchmark/runs/kimi-A/card.html","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/design/008-sk-design-parent/031-design-context-benchmark/runs/kimi-A/card.html","time":{"start":1782575908547,"end":1782575908555}},"id":"prt_f09ccfcaf001F9Uc0xGw7Ivso5","sessionID":"ses_0f633c972ffekahfiXQPo6WHxi","messageID":"msg_f09cc3c07001dKLaItiecqIGZK"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782575922181,"sessionID":"ses_0f633c972ffekahfiXQPo6WHxi","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"tool_6QgMOsKvG3F4vdIXIFk3OusF","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/design/008-sk-design-parent/031-design-context-benchmark/runs/kimi-A/notes.md","content":"# Design notes — Bestellimieten card\n\n## Constraints\n- Single self-contained HTML file, inline CSS only.\n- No external assets, no gradients, flat visual language.\n- Exact card size: 560 × 480 px.\n- Brand palette only.\n\n## Layout decisions\n- **Fixed card frame** with a single-pixel `var(--tint-300)` border; no shadows to keep the surface flat.\n- **Header band in brand blue** establishes hierarchy immediately and anchors the Anobel identity.\n- **Summary row** sits directly under the header so the three high-order numbers (total limit, total spent, remaining) are read before the table.\n- **Full-width alert banner** for the overspend condition; red is reserved exclusively for alerts.\n- **Table body** holds per-ship / per-location rows; sticky header keeps column labels visible if rows grow.\n\n## Color usage\n- `var(--blue)` / `var(--blue-deep)` for the header and primary brand presence.\n- `var(--tint-100)` for page background, `var(--white)` for card surface, `var(--tint-200/300)` for structural rules.\n- `var(--green)` only for positive remaining balances.\n- `var(--red)` only for the overspend alert, the negative remaining value, and the alert row highlight (5 % tint + left border).\n- `var(--gold)` used once for the near-limit row; kept rare as specified.\n- `var(--text)` (`#0a1a2f`) for body text; `var(--muted)` for secondary labels.\n\n## Typography\n- Font stack leads with `\"Hanken Grotesk\"`, falling back to system sans-serifs for self-contained rendering without an external font request.\n- Numeric values use `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums` so columns align cleanly.\n- Size scale: 20 px title, 18 px summary values, 14 px body, 12 px metadata, 10 px labels.\n\n## Data shape\n- Each row maps a location to a ship, then shows limit, spent, and remaining.\n- One row is healthy, one overspent, one near-limit — covering all three requested states.\n- Footer provides provenance without adding visual weight.\n\n## Accessibility / contrast\n- White text (`#fefefe`) on blue header and red alert meets high-contrast requirements.\n- Body text stays on white for maximum readability.\n- Alert uses both color and an icon to avoid relying on color alone.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/design/008-sk-design-parent/031-design-context-benchmark/runs/kimi-A/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/design/008-sk-design-parent/031-design-context-benchmark/runs/kimi-A/notes.md","time":{"start":1782575922176,"end":1782575922180}},"id":"prt_f09cdc6c5001SEQ0fc0oTIdmcM","sessionID":"ses_0f633c972ffekahfiXQPo6WHxi","messageID":"msg_f09cc3c07001dKLaItiecqIGZK"}}
